txt.en: Talk to Trennor to bypass the Skirmish Tutorials
'I'm Trennor, and I sit in a little bucket. Would you like to skip the Skirmish Tutorials?'
This is for folks who want to jump right into Skirmishes without the tutorials.
Trennor is outside of the Skirmish Camp in the Eyes and Guard Tavern.\n\nGo talk to Trennor. Nice Trennor always helps.
